    "description": "Vestige is a student-made game which won the first prize of the jury at College Lasalle Montreal.<br><br>Made in four months by a small team of four graduates, Vestige is an action/platforming game which offers vast liberty of movement.<br><br>Explore diverse and mysterious environments to discover new powers. With your Wall Jump, Dash, and Double Jump, uncover the secrets of an ancient, lost civilization.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>REACH YOUR OWN PATH</strong></h2><br><br>Using different platforming abilities, traverse difficult terrains and challenges. There is no finite way to reach your destination: the liberty is yours.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862960/extras/37d0a09844ca7755776f516bf00547f3.poster.avif?t=1642894152\" width=630 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862960/extras/37d0a09844ca7755776f516bf00547f3.webm?t=1642894152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862960/extras/37d0a09844ca7755776f516bf00547f3.mp4?t=1642894152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FAST-PACED ACTION</strong></h2><br><br>Hit and dodge your enemies in straightforward, but satisfying fast-paced combat.<br><br>By unlocking different upgrades, vanquish any enemies that stand in your way and create your own build based on your playstyle.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862960/extras/bcdc72a70417560adae2ecefeb6f7f73.poster.avif?t=1642894152\" width=630 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862960/extras/bcdc72a70417560adae2ecefeb6f7f73.webm?t=1642894152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862960/extras/bcdc72a70417560adae2ecefeb6f7f73.mp4?t=1642894152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EXPLORE THE WORLD</strong></h2><br><br>Up to 4 different zones are yours to explore, each with its own theme and ambiance. What secrets will you uncover?<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862960/extras/76878b31b275ac729c94a4c1a7f96808.poster.avif?t=1642894152\" width=630 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862960/extras/76878b31b275ac729c94a4c1a7f96808.webm?t=1642894152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862960/extras/76878b31b275ac729c94a4c1a7f96808.mp4?t=1642894152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
